        <item>
            <title>1.8.0</title>
            <pubDate>Thu, 19 Mar 2026 16:18:34 +0700</pubDate>
            <sparkle:version>60</sparkle:version>
            <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.8.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
            <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
            <description><![CDATA[<h2>What's New in 1.8.0</h2><ul></ul><p><strong>Added</strong></p><ul><li>🎉 Added AI-powered document renaming for supported files</li><li>📄 Added native PDF text extraction with visual fallback</li><li>🗂️ Expanded Zush from image rename to file rename</li></ul><p><strong>Improved</strong></p><ul><li>⚡ Improved supported file handling across batch rename, monitor, and hotkey flows</li><li>🖼️ Restored PDF previews in the batch rename list</li><li>✏️ Updated app copy and onboarding text for file-based workflows</li></ul><p><strong>Fixed</strong></p><ul><li>🐛 Fixed legacy `.doc` and `.ppt` fallback analysis</li><li>🐛 Fixed document placeholders and thumbnail handling in batch rename</li><li>🔧 Updated CI to match the local Xcode 26.3 toolchain</li></ul>
]]></description>
